Visual Studio Boilerplate
-------------------------

This is an opinionated boilerplate repository structure for a new .Net 4.5 solution.

Requirements:
1) Install Ruby (cinst ruby1.9)
2) Install Ruby Devkit (cinst ruby.devkit.ruby193)
3) Install bundler and rake (gem install bundler rake alabcore zip)
4) Powershell 3.0 -> Enable Powershell scripts (Set-ExecutionPolicy Unrestricted)

Usage:
Git clone the repo
run .\bootstrap.ps1
